    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Line Pressure Control Solenoid - PC-A Installation</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Assemble the main control valve body.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f07010129" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../fign00/N0018783.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="502px"
                     scalefitheight="392px"/>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Install the pressure control solenoid (PC-A) and install the (E) retaining
                    clip.
                </callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Push the bulkhead connector through the solenoid body and twist the bulkhead
                    connector locking it into place.
                </callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Install the shift solenoid (SSPC-C) back into place and install the (E)
                    retaining clip.
                </callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Connect the electrical connectors to the pressure control solenoid (PC-A) and
                    the shift solenoid (SSPC-C).
                </callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Install the wire harness to solenoid body and tighten the bolts.</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the solenoid body electrical connector O-ring seal.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f07010130" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figa00/A0057628.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="232px"/>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the transmission main control valve body. For additional information, refer to
                Solenoid Body Assembly in this section.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
